description: Overview* This High Resolution VGA Monitor Cable is designed to provide the highest video quality possible through VGA.* Ideally suited for high resolution VGA applications, this high quality male to male coaxial VGA cable eliminates picture "ghosting" and fuzzy images inherent to non-coaxial cables, and provides superior EMI interference protection by using ferrite cores near the connector ends.Specifications* Connectors: Gold-plated HD15 Male* Conductor: 100% Bare Copper, No Copper Clad Steel (CCS)* Resolutions: Supports UXGA (1600x1200), WXGA (1680x1050), 1080p (1920x1080) and up* Jacket: PVC* Gauge: 28 AWG* Shielding: Double Shielded Cable Structure to Eliminate Interferences* RoHS Compliance: Yes
title: Cable Matters Gold Plated VGA Monitor Cable with Ferrites 6 Feet, 100% Bare Copper
